title: SEAL It with a Kiss
description:
A woman in the SEALs?Lieutenant Tabitha Chapel is determined to become the first woman to join the navy SEALs. She'll use every connection she has (and she has plenty), any wile (feminine or otherwise) and her substantial strength of will to make this happen.
Not in this man's navy!
Commander Marc Miller is equally determined to keep women in general - and Tabitha Chapel in particular - out of the SEALs. There are a lot of things he's like to do with Tabby, and being her commanding officer isn't one of them.But the commander is about to learn that Tabby's woman enough to take everything he doles out and more...
author: Rogenna Brewer
